{
  "stem": "1692.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They are calling us.'",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother said, 'I don't want to see.' But when she finally got up, there was a young SS man standing up on a jeep, calling them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He asked them, 'Do you believe in God?' And when they said, yes, he let them go.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the two men from the last three graves, were held back and shot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of them was my uncle, my mother's brother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And although my mother was killed anyway-- I have-- if she didn't come home that night, I would have never forgiven myself, because I urged her to go to the sick.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] [SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was on top of the grave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like they set them in lines one person backed up between the legs of the person behind them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the last three graves, they didn't touch it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As they stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They used to use all kinda trick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they stopped, and that's when the SS man was calling them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just-- just before it was her turn to be shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, and that's why she didn't want to get up when her sister started to say they're calling us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "An idea?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because that's-- that-- they did all kinds of thing to Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One time, they would do that, and the next time, they would grab a man with a beard and pull him in the street.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no special reason-- just-- at Hitler's way-- just being sadistic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the-- but the SS man actually saved her life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he-- that was really-- he saved the-- the-- the two graves, just And he didn't really save them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He saved them for later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because he didn't-- all the people were killed but the Ukrainian who dug graves.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
